text = "You’re walking down the dimly lit 
streets at night on your way home. 
Since it’s getting awfully fast 
dark, you decide to take a shortcut 
through one of the allies you’re
passing by. As you walk past a row 
of dumpsters you see a gang of 
skinheads, some leaning against 
the wall others just huddling 
around a burning trash bin. As you 
get closer the biggest one of them 
notices you and calls out: “Hey,
what’s your business here tranny? 
Don’t you know you’re not welcome 
around these parts?” His gaze and 
aggressive stance makes it very 
obvious that you still don’t fully 
pass yet and can be clocked by 
disgusting men like him. Just as 
you’re about to reply another one
of the group speaks up in a deep 
growly voice “Piss off to your 
jewish friends before we beat the 
shit out of you, you sick fuck. 
Or wait… maybe we might just do 
that anyways!” You shiver at 
hearing the men’s cruel laughter.
How will you respond?
Run away
Prepare for a fight
Try to argue your way out
"

